text: Escape to a serene and peaceful retreat on 7.49 stunning acres, surrounded by nature's beauty. This property features an orchard with fruit trees, plenty of garden space, a dedicated camping area with cozy firepit, and a refreshing swim pondperfect for outdoor enthusiasts. The 2, 709 sq ft manufactured home offers 3 spacious bedrooms plus 2 additional bonus rooms with closets, unbelievable storage, wired for generator. A 3-car garage, additional shop plus plenty of space for your RV, boat and other toys! Wander through fields of dreams, under the shade of mature cedars, and discover the tranquility of country living!

Charming updated 1954 home sits on .29 acres with some hint's of cabin styling. Open ceilings with sturdy beams, updated kitchen and bath. There is an east side sunroom that has a utility room adjacent. The sunroom is not part of the 888SF. Head accross the back yard and your will find a garage with work room and garage for the car. Behind the garage is a metal RV Cover that can keep your toys out of the weather. The back yard has an apple tree and space for a vegetable garden. A very private setting and access to the back yard, garage and Rv Cover via Azalea Lane. The home faces West and looks out to acres and acres of farmland. Super easy access to Hwy 20 and I-5. Schools, services, shopping and entertainment just minutes away.

Nestled in the serene Nookachamp subdivision, this superb 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home features uninterrupted views of the Cascade foothills. Enjoy this meticulously maintained garden paradise with a greenhouse. Entertain with ease using the gas-connected grill on your wrap around deck. The home boasts top-tier quality throughout, from 2 separate spacious living areas to the gourmet kitchen. The bonus room is perfect for a home office or a flexible guest room. A true Nookachamp delight and a dream home for those seeking tranquility and a view. Retire to your over-sized primary suite with walk-in shower and closet. This home has no shortage of custom upgrades, dont miss the workshop in the outdoor basement!

Unlock the potential of this spacious, vacant lot situated in the vibrant heart of Concrete, Washington. Nestled in a charming, small-town setting with stunning natural surroundings, this property offers a unique opportunity for your dream project or investment. Concrete is known for its picturesque landscapes and outdoor recreational opportunities. Make this your Next Home.

Welcome to Bucko Estates a new legacy community! The Hattie is a 2 story home with 3 bed/2.25ba + Bonus room & office with a modern farmhouse vibe. This home has over $23K in upgrades. The main level has a great room w/gas fireplace w/wood mantle & is open to the dining room & kitchen. The kitchen has 36 upper cabinets that are off white & lower Ember color on Maple cabinets. There is also a gas range, & island. This home has all quartz countertops! Upstairs has 3 bedrooms, a bonus room & laundry room. The primary bedroom has TWO walk in closets & ensuite bathroom w/tile shower, tile floor & double sinks! There is a covered patio out back. The yard is fully landscaped & the backyard is fenced. This home has a 3 CAR GARAGE!

Move in ready! Nicely updated inside & out, top to bottom, in the town of La Conner! Too much to list here. Located within walking distance of all the shops, restaurants, water front, and everything else La Conner has to offer. Home features single level living and was completely gone through in 2019. New roof, new furnace, new Hardi Plank siding, new insulation in the crawl space & attic, kitchen & bathrooms were all remodeled, and the list goes on and on. Agent has a full list of the upgrades done. This home sits on a corner lot w/2 large storage sheds w/power, a covered car port that also has storage cabinets built in and extra room to park a boat or RV. City said it was possible to build a garage w/apartment. Buyer to verify all.

This well-cared-for 3BR, 2BA single wide offers plenty of space & natural light in a great location, minutes from downtown Mount Vernon and medical plus walking distance to Haggen. No age restriction park has tons of street parking near unit for guests and great walkability. Ready for your cosmetic updates, this home has been lovingly cared for over the years and is in great condition. The siding has been recently painted giving a lovely curb appeal boost, and inside youll enjoy single-level-living with a generously sized kitchen and main living space. Your carport and shed are perfect for car and hobby storage. Must have park approval before submitting offers.

Come and enjoy this spacious townhouse near downtown Anacortes! This home features vaulted ceilings, an open layout, and large windows for natural light. The main floor has a generous kitchen with shaker cabinets and ample storage. Welcoming everyone with a zero-step entry, plus a main level bedroom/bath for convenience Upstairs, enjoy the loft as an additional family room, and upper deck boasting views of the bay and Mount Baker, plus hot tub hookup! The oversized primary bedroom includes a walk-in closet and en suite bathroom. This home also has a private two-car garage, patio, RV parking, and a bonus flex area ideal for a home office or hobby space.This 2-unit building is nestled in a peaceful Anacortes neighborhood with a gorgeous yard!

Incredible multi-use property in serene setting w mountain views includes shop, barn, stable, equestrian space, & more. Spacious home features tons of windows, wood beam ceiling & hardwood floors throughout. Primary bedroom includes a barn door, huge slider to full length deck, walk-in closet, & spa like bath w dual waterfall sinks & soaking tub. Downstairs enjoy the built-in wet bar, cozy fireplace, & additional bedrooms. Outside enjoy the partially fenced yard w fruit trees, garden space, & expansive pasture. Plenty of space for your horses & other animals w shop, barn, stable, chicken condominium, & outbuildings. Detached garage & carport, & RV parking.

Welcome to this charming, cozy Wildflower home! The large, bright, open living room features a vaulted ceiling and plenty of space to relax and unwind. The galley-style kitchen has a window and convenient oversized sink. Look out the window to a deck where you can enjoy your morning coffee! Primary bedroom has its own access to the bathroom that is shared in the hallway along with a second bedroom. A laundry room can also be found conveniently placed near the center of the home. The patio off the living room is great for entertaining and features space for seating and your own BBQ. The yard features garden space, a fire pit, and mature landscaping. A single car garage is located in walking distance. Come make this place your very own!

This exceptional property offers the perfect blend of convenience, tranquility, & valley views. Situated on spacious acreage, it provides the ideal setting for peaceful living while being in town. The main home boasts a generous kitchen, a welcoming living room w/ a wood fireplace insert, & a bright sunroom. The lower level expands your living space w/ a large family room featuring a cozy gas fireplace insert, full bath, 2 additional finished rooms, & a walk-out patio w/ parking & separate entrance. In addition, a secondary manufactured home on the property is perfect for guests or a potential rental income opportunity. Transform this great home into your dream home on property that offers many possibilities.

Live in Luxury in your new custom built home perched on the side of a hill nestled up to several acres of greenbelt providing lots of privacy, and nature at its best. Relax among the trees and enjoy lots of natural light with the sun rays streaming through your great room as you look out on the territorial views from your deck. Enjoy the PNW lifestyle with community activities such as golf, tennis, pickleball, swimming, a club house and BBQ area, providing endless opportunities for recreation and socializing. Explore the beauty of two private beaches and take advantage of the free boat ramp, enhancing your waterfront lifestyle. Additional perks include moorage and a six-acre storage lot. It's more than just a home it's a lifestyle.

Welcome to the Prairie Acres community! This lovely home with a charming wrap-around porch is the one you've been waiting for! The main level boasts a large living room with built-in shelving & a cozy wood stove. The formal dining area accommodates large gatherings & leads into a spacious kitchen with ample counter & storage space. Next to the kitchen is a large breakfast area, laundry/pantry & a sizable rec-room with a wet bar. The primary bedroom offers an ensuite bath & a walk-in closet. Additionally, there are two guest bedrooms & a full guest bath. Outside, a huge 2, 232 SF heated shop with an office awaits, along with a 432 SF multipurpose building. The 1.19-acres feature mature landscaping & space for your RV, tools & all your toys!

Gardener's paradise! Beautiful landscaping surrounds this charming 3 bedroom, 1 3/4 bath rambler in desirable Skyline neighborhood. Lots of natural light and great room feel. Open kitchen, dining area and living room with adjoining sunroom. Living room features a gas log fireplace and vaulted ceiling with a skylight. Sunroom opens to a spacious 2 level deck to enjoy the private, fully fenced gorgeous backyard and partial water view. Gas bbq hook-up on small patio. Even a fancy chicken coop! 1 car garage with good storage, workbench and EV plug in. RV parking with waste outlet in front graveled area. Close to Skyline amenities. Something for everyone!

This stunning 2, 022 sq. ft. rambler offers an inviting open concept layout with 3 bedrooms plus office. Enjoy designer finishes throughout, including a charming covered front porch and rear patio. The gourmet kitchen boasts elegant quartz countertops, soft-close cabinets and large island, making it a chefs dream. This home is thoughtfully upgraded with LED under-cabinet lighting, painted wood cased windows, and a convenient patio gas stub for outdoor entertaining. You'll appreciate the practicality of a sink in the laundry room, central A/C. Outside, the property is fully fenced and beautifully landscaped, creating a private oasis. Enjoy access to community amenities, including multiple parks and trails, perfect for outdoor adventures.

Plenty of room to live and grow in this air-conditioned 3-br single-level home in the Blackburn Ridge community. It's ideally located close to Hillcrest Park and local schools. This is a great starter home or an easy-to-manage residence. The primary bedroom has a private double-sink bath with walk-in shower. The spacious kitchen has a large breakfast nook overlooking the back yard. Spend afternoons on the covered back porch watching birds in the lush forest behind the home. Little Mountain views from the front. Plenty of room for additional storage in the garage, with a pull-down ladder to create more space above the semi-finished garage. Great for commuters, with only one minute to I-5, and 60 minutes to Seattle! Move-in condition!

This well maintained key turn ready home located in the desired Skagit Highlands is one that you don't want to miss! This 3-bed, 2.5-bath residence is packed with upgrades, including a brand-new furnace, AC Unit for the hot summer days, Stainless Oven, dishwasher, and a newer water heater which takes away the worry of replacing them in the near future. Stylish new light fixtures and ceiling fans add modern elegance. The fully fenced backyard offers a private area that is perfect for relaxation or entertaining. Enjoy parks and trails nearby, with easy access to the freeway, groceries, and restaurants. Don't waitschedule your viewing today and seize the opportunity to own this move-in-ready gem in a prime location!

This is a once in a lifetime opportunity to own waterfront real estate in the historic town of La Conner, WA. The gateway to the incredible San Juan Islands. A boaters dream with your own 96ft deep water dock. Exquisite views of the Swinomish Channel and Iconic Rainbow Bridge. A year round Pacific Northwest lifestyle with access to world class crabbing, fishing, and island hopping. This beautiful cottage was updated in 2022 to include High end finishes and Contemporary Esthetics with the outdoor living space and breathtaking views. Incredible potential for a future remodel that has zoning for a 3 story home. Enjoy panoramic views of Mt Baker and the Swinomish Channel. Zoned commercial/grandfathered resi. Dont miss out on this opportunity

Enjoy classic charm in this better than new 2 story built in 2022. This enchanting home welcomes you inside w/an inviting warmth, Easterly water views & bold views of Mt Baker. Open concept packed full of amenities such as quartz thru out kitchen & bathrooms, hardwood thru out main level & upstairs primary bdrm. Tile floors in bathrooms & neutral carpet in two bdms. Spacious kitchen w/ large island, deck off dining rm, upstairs primary bdrm w/bath, large walk-in closet & deck for enjoying the mesmerizing water & mt views. 2 addtl bedrooms upstairs share a Jack n Jill bath. Centrally located in town, nestled in a calm, serene setting featuring a low maintenance fully fenced yard, detached garage w/alley access & addtl RV/boat parking.

Come and see this property featuring 3 beds / 1 bath, a bonus space and a lovely backyard perfect for relaxation and entertainment. The modern kitchen has updated granite countertops, while the recently renovated bathroom offers a stylish & refreshed space. Enjoy gorgeous laminate flooring throughout all the living areas and a feature wood wall that adds warmth and character. The home also has new windows that enhance energy efficiency and natural light. Step outside to a huge deck, ideal for entertaining, and a serene, private backyard. With RV parking and close proximity to shopping, restaurants, and easy access to I-5, this home offers both convenience and comfort. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity!

Enjoy country-living with tranquil, lush, verdant surroundings at this custom-built home, which sits on 4.65 park-like acres in one of Bows best neighborhoods. The immaculately maintained 4-bdrm, 3 bath, 3700+/- sq ft home includes a fenced garden, greenhouses, an orchard with fruit trees & berries and forest trails. Inside, you will find main floor living with the primary bedroom, living & dining room area. Be cozy and enjoy the natural views from the large windows in the eat-in kitchen. Upstairs 3 spacious bedrooms (two with ensuite bathrooms) and large office with storage room. There is also a large sun-lit bonus room that can be used as a play area, a creative space, studio etc. 3 car garage. Detailed update/maintenance records.

Indulge in luxury with sweeping bay, island, and mountain views from this exquisite residence. The dramatic two-story living room, complete with a catwalk and loft, sets a tone of elegance. A gourmet kitchen features granite countertops, a built-in wine rack, & a gas stovetop, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. The opulent main floor primary suite offers a vaulted ceiling, deck access, a spacious walk-in closet, & a lavish ensuite bath. Upper-level bedrooms share a Jack & Jill bath. The expansive lower level includes a rec room, theater room, kitchen, bedroom, & bath. Outside, the meticulous landscape features a pond, cascading waterfall, inviting patios, and winding paths. This home blends elegance, comfort, and breathtaking natural beauty.

Check out this beautifully maintained 4 bedroom 3 bathroom home on almost half an acre, tucked away yet close to shopping, dining & I-5. The main level features a large living room with a gas fireplace, open to the dining room, a spacious kitchen with the utility room and guest bath off of it, 3 bedrooms & a full bathroom. The second story is a primary suite with a full bath, walk-in closet, sitting space & a private balcony. The upstairs could be used as a flex space, multi-generational living, or a potential ADU. The oversized 1-car garage offers plenty of storage options. Additional off-street parking with room for a boat or RV. The electrical panel was upgraded in 2023. Spacious fully fenced back yard with a patio & mature landscaping.

Welcome to Brickyard Park a new 55+ Community! This home is COMPLETED & is a 3 bed/1.75 ba single story townhome with over 20K in upgrades. It has a vaulted great room w/gas fireplace. Kitchen has upgraded white cabinets, gas range, dw, micro hood & quartz counters. Primary ensuite has a vaulted ceiling, wic, & quartz countertops in the bath. LVP flooring & upgraded carpet. Comfort height toilets. Garage & walls are insulated for sound. Single car garage. The HOA maintains your yard, irrigation & fences. HOA owns fences. There is a covered rear patio w/ a gas hookup. Clubhouse has an almost 1 acre park w/a walking trail around it. There is a pickleball ct, horseshoes, & bocce ball. Pics are of a diff. home.

Step into this beautifully updated 2-bedroom, 1-bath house on a quiet street. The elegantly designed bathroom features a double sink vanity, perfect for shared use, while the newer roof, brand-new water heater, and electrical provide peace of mind. This home boasts sleek vinyl plank flooring throughout for a modern, easy-to-maintain aesthetic. The heart of the home is the stunning kitchen, equipped with granite countertops and new appliances, ideal for cooking and entertaining. Additional features include walk-in closets and an oversized laundry room for ample storage. Dont miss this opportunityschedule a showing today!

Upgrades galore in this beautiful cabin in the woods. Additions include: new floors, new plumbing, new hot water heater, new patio framing, new well pump, outdoor kitchen, outdoor shower, firewood shed. Turnkey rental sold with all furniture and accessories. Keep it as an Airbnb or use it as your vacation getaway. Airbnb financial information available upon request. A truly one-of-a-kind property straight out of a movie. Lots of value in the land and the setting, a small creek runs just north of the house as well.

Ready to move right in & enjoy this two story craftsman in a delightful neighborhood featuring community trails. Welcomed with sky-high ceilings into an open living boasting updated lighting, wonderful kitchen with oversized eat at island, ss appliances & walk-in pantry. Flowing layout thru the kitchen, living & dining areas with convenient door to back patio. Upstairs offers generous landing for additional use, vaulted ceiling primary with french doors, en-suite & walk-in closet, 3 more bedrooms, full bath & laundry all on this level for ease of living. Outside is extra great & gardeners delight with greenhouse, multiple fruit trees, vegetables, lush landscaping plus play areas, large deck & covered patio brings this outdoor space to life.

Step into this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom rambler with a fully fenced backyard and a covered patio, perfect for entertaining. Enjoy the serene surroundings of apple trees, berry bushes, and space for your own garden. The spacious primary bedroom boasts a large walk-in closet and a private bathroom, while the living area exudes a sense of openness with its vaulted ceiling. This property is conveniently located just minutes from schools, parks, and downtown Sedro Woolley, and offers easy access to I-5 for commuters. Nestled at the end of a cul-de-sac, directly across from the community park, this is the perfect place to call home.

Welcome to your charming A-frame retreat at Lake Cavanaugh! This cozy 680 sq ft home, built in 1974 and updated in 2007, blends rustic charm with modern convenience. Nestled on a spacious 12, 632 sq ft secluded lot, this private property features two driveways, a 144 sq ft deck, an existing fire pit, and a cleared area ideal for a gazebo or second fire pit. A small storage shed offers a loft, workbench, dryer, & plumbing/power for a future washer. Fully furnished, the property includes a private well, hot/cold outdoor faucets, a pressure tank, hot water tank, and a generator hook-up. An approved design for a 2-bedroom septic system is provided. Under 2 miles from the boat launch, your tranquil lake life awaits!

Beautiful, large corner lot property has a 3 bedroom home in the heart of downtown Burlington. This includes the area West of the two car garage to the fence. This home has been completely remodeled - everything is new down to the foundation. Gorgeous quartz countertops, new appliances, large kitchen with spacious cabinets, flooring and roof. There is a detached 2 car garage with lots of storage space. an easy walk into town, the park, and local restaurants. Upstairs has a bedroom and a family room/den/office/game room which is all carpeted. To the west side of the garage is a large additional yard area.

Discover carefree living in the Willow floorplan, nestled within Woodside's 55+ community. This single-level home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and an open great room perfect for entertaining. The modern kitchen features a granite island and ample counter space. Enjoy outdoor relaxation on your private patio. A 2-car garage provides convenient parking. Experience low-maintenance living with HOA-managed landscaping and irrigation. Community amenities include a lodge and park. Don't miss this opportunity to own a home in a vibrant community.

Welcome to your charming Cape Cod retreat with breathtaking water views and a prime location near Guemes Trail and the beach. This 3-bedroom home features a den/office, 2.5 baths, and hardwood floors that accentuate its cozy appeal. With an abundance of windows, the interior is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Step outside to the front porch or the lovely rear deck to take in the vistas of the water and Cypress Island. Watch the ferry and boats pass by as you unwind and savor the stunning sunsets with your favorite beverage in hand. A delightful garden, offering the perfect blend of comfort and natural beauty. Don't miss the opportunity to make this haven your own. Exterior painting recently completed!

Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 1.75-bath rambler situated on a spacious, level lot. This home boasts abundant yard space perfect for outdoor activities. Recent updates include a newer roof, hardboard siding, furnace, and windows, ensuring long-lasting quality and efficiency. Enjoy the cedar deck off the kitchen and the patio space with a fenced backyard, ideal for relaxation and entertaining. While the house needs interior paint, flooring, and general cosmetic improvements, it presents a fantastic opportunity to bring your personal touches and make it your own. Whether youre an investor or a first-time homebuyer, dont miss out on this diamond in the rough with immense potential!

Discover a captivating condo boasting partial views and a distinctive layout featuring a sunken living room, creating a cozy ambiance. The kitchen dazzles with stainless steel appliances and a convenient island offering additional seating. Retreat to the primary bedroom oasis, complete with an ensuite showcasing a luxurious deep, jetted tub, a separate shower, and a double sink vanity. Positioned perfectly for outdoor enthusiasts, this gem offers easy access to walking trails, state parks, and the vibrant heart of town. Welcome home to a haven where comfort and convenience intersect effortlessly.
